ratings.comment: Sra. Nenn was a great TA. I learned a lot by going to her office hours and she's very easy to approach. She held review sessions outside of class time for the midterm and final which was very helpful as well.

Señorita Nenn was an incredible teacher! I learned so much from taking her class, a lot more than I ever did in high school. She was always open to helping her students and really wanted everyone to succeed. I am so glad I was able to have her as my Spanish teacher. Overall, great teacher. HIGHLY recommended.

Señora Nenn was awesome! She held review sessions out of class and was always available to talk. I can't stress how much I learned in her class. Sra Nenn is an amazing TA and if you have the opportunity, I highly recommend taking her section.

Señorita Nenn is an outstanding TA for Spanish 204! I cannot even begin to articulate how much I highly recommend her. I learned so much, and the class was very enjoyable -- even at 745. She held extra review sessions and was always around to answer questions. Take her!
Srta Nenn was awesome!  Our class was fun every day and you could tell she wanted her students to succeed.  If you have the chance, I'd go for her section.

Srta Nenn was a really great Spanish TA. She held study sessions outside of class before the midterm and final and was super helpful both in class and out. She sincerely cares about her students.  Class was always fun to go to and I learned more in one semester with her than I did in four years of high school.
